00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:44.460
We are also using a pen, as you can see, to move some objects

00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:48.670
It's also based on infrared technology, and it's really cool

00:00:48.670 --> 00:00:53.150
There is a 3D skeleton that pops out of the screen

00:00:53.150 --> 00:00:56.830
It has a high detail level and a very good resolution, 1080p

00:00:56.830 --> 00:01:00.370
Here we can see Elena using an anatomy app

00:01:00.370 --> 00:01:05.110
