00:01:05.110 --> 00:01:08.420
And it can be seen on a scren on the left

00:01:08.420 --> 00:01:11.840
You also see that screen in front of you, it's awesome

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:16.050
This is really cool for education

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:18.120
And this is me

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:23.650
